import math

def fake_calculator_sum(a, b):
    multiplier = 2
    result = 0
    while a or b:
        bit_sum = a % 10 + b % 10
        bit_sum %= 10
        result += bit_sum * multiplier
        a = math.floor(a / 10)
        b = math.floor(b / 10)
        multiplier *= 10
    return result
